></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一啲都唔好食<br />\n芋圓又細粒又無味<br />\n反而豪大大仲好過佢</blockquote><br />\n我都覺，啲芋圓、蕃薯圓只係上左色，食落只係有陣糯米粉味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係平囉，廿五蚊碗。<br />\n<br />\n我之前係一田買左一包台灣農協會造既蕃薯圓，黃色包裝，大約三十蚊，佢有三隻色的蕃薯，黃、橙、紫，食落好有蕃薯香，而且一啲添加劑都無落，強烈推介大家買黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8cfaa0a5df28516d057d1abd17905ce1476ea1","tid":89902,"uid":583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食過深水埗康瑞<br />\n好食係好食<br />\n不過好細碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有無好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一啲都唔好食<br />\n芋圓又細粒又無味<br />\n反而豪大大仲好過佢</blockquote><br />\n我都覺，啲芋圓、蕃薯圓只係上左色，食落只係有陣糯米粉味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係平囉，廿五蚊碗。<br />\n<br />\n我之前係一田買左一包台灣農協會造既蕃薯圓，黃色包裝，大約三十蚊，佢有三隻色的蕃薯，黃、橙、紫，食落好有蕃薯香，而且一啲添加劑都無落，強烈推介大家買黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到買？"},{"pid":"ccf065088c1b3454c0ac58f1f95519562e12cf96","tid":89902,"uid":7169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一啲都唔好食<br />\n芋圓又細粒又無味<br />\n反而豪大大仲好過佢</blockquote><br />\n我都覺，啲芋圓、蕃薯圓只係上左色，食落只係有陣糯米粉味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係平囉，廿五蚊碗。<br />\n<br />\n我之前係一田買左一包台灣農協會造既蕃薯圓，黃色包裝，大約三十蚊，佢有三隻色的蕃薯，黃、橙、紫，食落好有蕃薯香，而且一啲添加劑都無落，強烈推介大家買黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到買？</blockquote><br />\n唔係寫左一田咩"},{"pid":"e6ce4c59cdfe844bc613755a36b8044efaae62ef","tid":89902,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我都覺，啲芋圓、蕃薯圓只係上左色，食落只係有陣糯米粉味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係平囉，廿五蚊碗。<br />\n<br />\n我之前係一田買左一包台灣農協會造既蕃薯圓，黃色包裝，大約三十蚊，佢有三隻色的蕃薯，黃、橙、紫，食落好有蕃薯香，而且一啲添加劑都無落，強烈推介大家買黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到買？</blockquote><br />\n唔係寫左一田咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但佢整個配搭都好正<br />\n有咩勁人有食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想自己瘋狂煮黎食！"},{"pid":"b0c7ad0227d8e22e5d2ed2adb989d957f884c602","tid":89902,"uid":58471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQp2AZ4zQsJ9jKMYANQvh6gBhKc2jZyqEwTzobf4HJP3Y?filename=qV2KE54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqV2KE54.jpg&h=9b782c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台北食既 $25 大碗到兩個人食都食唔哂<br />\n好想再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0e7ed7f94eb1b5fbf6d49c9f1ac7819b703c77","tid":89902,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n食過荃灣豪大大 三十蚊黎講真係唔差 兩個人share食都得<br />\n<br />\nbtw 想問仙草同三色q果邊度有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想試下自己整芋圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ab8fc376805758502485b368a149b79a4b768a","tid":89902,"uid":38895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"自已整芋圓好易<br />\n買芋頭同生粉/木薯粉跟個人口味比例整<br />\n整完切粒，放入滾水一陣，浮起後配糖水/碎冰完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbb55bac511e135ec7bb825e0d839642a62048f","tid":89902,"uid":15144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:59:31.000Z","msg":"荃灣松記 最近先有得食 $6 8粒 可以加落啲糖水到 加幾多份都得 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好有番薯同芋頭味 同埋好煙韌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dec32a01691186aeb3b49ac4d1af48a24bba2e9","tid":89902,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T19:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQp2AZ4zQsJ9jKMYANQvh6gBhKc2jZyqEwTzobf4HJP3Y?filename=qV2KE54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqV2KE54.jpg&h=9b782c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台北食既 $25 大碗到兩個人食都食唔哂<br />\n好想再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間"},{"pid":"a4c434148c0aab8ad2399d9284609342da04b850","tid":89902,"uid":8063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豪大大雞扒 荃灣果間<br />\n好似話幾好食 但我未食過 想試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好食又平又大碗"}]}